imdb.plot outline: Filmed in front of a a live studio audience from the 12th floor of the Mont Bleu Resort Casino and Spa in beautiful South Lake Tahoe, online talk show Wake Up Tahoe provides information, weather, events, updates, music and current events geared to locals, former locals, and vacationers to the area. Partnered with Tahoe South, Getaway Reno Tahoe, Fabulous Lake Tahoe, and many others, local celebrity Dreu Murin provides laughs as the host, while he talks with unique and new quests every day. Adra Janean brings you your weather daily, as well as the last segment of every episode. Wednesdays are always cooking days, make sure to see what Adra whips up this week!
